<h1>{{ title }}</h1>

<p>
Last year I published the first HTMHell advent calendar with 24 links to articles about HTML I found on other sites. Since many people enjoyed these posts, I decided to raise the ante and <strong>publish</strong> 24 articles on HTMHell written specifically for the advent calendar.
</p>
<p>
24 authors from all over the world (Austria, France, Germany, India, Italy, The Netherlands, UK, USA) gave their best and wrote about accessibility, performance, usability, and security. Starting December 1st, you can read a new article every day until December 24th.
</p>
<p>
Thanks a lot to the authors for writing and <a href="https://ericwbailey.design/">Eric W. Bailey</a> who helped me with reviewing.
</p>
<p>
I hope you enjoy reading the posts as much as I did!
</p>
